name: D R E A M E R
description:
This is the fourth piece out of my new series. Each piece comes with a small quotes about how I’m feeling about life at the moment of creation. 

D R E A M E R 

“ something big is coming my way and I’m going head first ”

My life has been put on hold for the past 3 years and now I’ve decided to throw myself in the deep end. This is so frightening to me but I’m excited for the adventure; Things will start moving fast but I won’t let it overwhelm me. 

I have also chosen to use penguins to represent myself as they are my favourite animal.
